                    <span>After 43 years of reading this is it--the finest book I have ever experienced. One aspect that I don't see mentioned in other review is just how damned funny the book is. I could hardly believe the first few jokes and then they started coming rapidly.  There is a growing sense of doom as you near a conclusion that made me cry. It will be hard to read other books now that I've seen how it really can be.</span>
                  
              
